g car seat that will work for children up to 2 years old.","The SnugRide comes with extra padding to secure premature newborns, and its simple harness and headrest adjusts for your growing child. This carrier fits a wide range of strollers and has machine-washable cushions. The <a href=\"/best-baby-car-seats\">baby car seat</a> is large and heavy, so it is cumbersome in compact cars. Still, its adjustable base and reclining seat make it the best infant car seat we reviewed and the winner of our Top Ten Reviews Gold Award."]},"id":"4c4f4a99-ece4-45b1-87b4-2487abb5f05c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Safety"},"id":"f07c38af-cc73-48e5-82c5-249716878956","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/87fxNrFjuPpEeUskfx89aA.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Since experts agree that young children should ride rear-facing as long possible, Graco has designed this seat to fit your baby from the first car ride until age 2. The Graco SnugRide 40 takes the best aspects of convertible car seats and packs it into an exclusively rear-facing seat.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/53452-graco-snugride-352.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/87fxNrFjuPpEeUskfx89aA.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"87fxNrFjuPpEeUskfx89aA","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/87fxNrFjuPpEeUskfx89aA.jpg","alt":""},"id":"a873c7d6-a9ed-4f18-9207-ff75136e64d3","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["For example, many convertible car seats include a reclining seat, so you can adjust the seat without any hassle. The SnugRide&#39;s adjustable base and carrier allow you to recline the seat for a child up to 40 pounds while remaining in a rear-facing position. Also, the base includes a footrest, so you won&#39;t have to worry about your little one grind her feet on your seat backs. Most convertible car seats also have a simple adjustable headrest and harness, so you wouldn&#39;t have to rethread the seatbelts every month. The SnugRide includes a no-rethread system with 15 positions to make sure the seat grows with your child.","In addition to keeping your child in a rear-facing position until she is 2 years old, the Graco SnugRide 40 includes a five-point harness, side-impact protection and energy-absorbent foam. The base has a level indicator to minimize user error. While this toddler car seat does have LATCH connectors, they are not the simple one-click buckles that many other car seats include. Finally, the SnugRide is airplane compliant, although you&#39;ll always want to review the owner&#39;s manual before your trip to make sure you have everything you need."]},"id":"aafe1cfb-5945-4fc7-9cbf-afef0b196d2c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Convenience"},"id":"cc32c012-25b7-421d-a1ce-c3b2972b6a86","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/JqHdF5X5rTBWqgJHGuPhXY.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Although safety is your top priority in picking a car seat, you&#39;d be hard pressed to find a baby car seat that does not include any of the standard safety features we look for. Instead, most parents want to make sure they can actually live with their new car seat. The Graco SnugRide 40 goes a long way to make sure you and your child are comfortable for the next two years.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/53452-graco-snugride-359.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JqHdF5X5rTBWqgJHGuPhXY.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"JqHdF5X5rTBWqgJHGuPhXY","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JqHdF5X5rTBWqgJHGuPhXY.jpg","alt":""},"id":"c64cb3ec-329b-4213-a88c-ba550d2d3e40","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The SnugRide uses Graco&#39;s Click &amp; Connect technology to make it compatible with many strollers. It is easy to disconnect the car seat from the base and transfer it to your stroller. In fact, unlike many other car seats, you do not have to tilt the seat as you disconnect it from the base.","The car seat has all of the standard convenience features you would expect. The adjustable carry handle is comfortable and rotates in many different directions for any need. You can keep the base in the car for the life of the car seat. Also, it comes with simple installation instructions.","The best feature, though, is its machine-washable cushions. You can take off the cushion, throw it in the washing machine and hand-wash the shell and seatbelts. Unfortunately, you cannot remove the seatbelts, which is a minor hassle, but you can still get everything clean without much fuss.","One thing to consider with this car seat is that it is bulkier than most other car seats, and at just under 10 pounds, moving it can become cumbersome. If you have a 20-pound baby, the car seat will weigh a total of 30 pounds. It&#39;s likely that you&#39;ll end up leaving the carrier attached to the base as your child gets older, and it is harder to get a child into a rear-facing car seat as they get older and larger. It&#39;s a minor inconvenience, but it&#39;s something you should keep in mind."]},"id":"8d9bd1cc-077b-405e-aae9-4a955f193006","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Additional Features"},"id":"8b5262ae-f09c-4227-9511-a44d54bb6e01","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/LBUWGovhEQJ2c9gadsKkmF.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The SnugRide 40 includes all of the standard additional features we look for. Its reclining seat and adjustable head support allow the newborn car seat to grow with your baby. It has a center-pull adjustment to tighten the harness before your trip, and the canopy includes an extra flap to offer more protection against the elements.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/53452-graco-snugride-354.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LBUWGovhEQJ2c9gadsKkmF.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"LBUWGovhEQJ2c9gadsKkmF","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LBUWGovhEQJ2c9gadsKkmF.jpg","alt":""},"id":"532890e3-5fe3-4900-9cce-d87ac5f0eaca","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Despite taking many cues from convertible car seats, the SnugRide does not include an attached or optional cup holder. It&#39;s not a big issue, but when you have a 1-year-old child, he might want a snack or drink during the car ride."]},"id":"903edf7a-fe54-41d9-83b2-e4420e49b29f","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"c2e88f77-0872-4859-a597-4b1dff4f8e47","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Graco SnugRide 40 comes with a one-year warranty, which is standard for most baby car seats. It comes with a user manual that you can store in the seat, but if you lose it, you can download a new one online. Finally, if you need to contact customer support, the Graco website provides email and phone contact."]},"id":"a19470d0-cc23-402e-80b2-d5f81df7bfd7","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"f77f9c95-e34c-4e43-b60d-54fcc266ef1c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Graco SnugRide 40 is the best infant car seat because it secures your child in a rear-facing position until she is 2 years old. The carrier is compatible with many strollers, and the cushions are machine washable. The SnugRide takes the best elements from convertible car seats to create the safest, most convenient car seat we reviewed."]},"id":"12f0d5b9-78a4-437a-8311-273d01dabf8c","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_53480","url":"/graco-snugride-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"grant-morgan","url":"/author/grant-morgan","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Grant Morgan","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"5h9THR5HH34dskUikqZYj8","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2011-08-23T01:38:35Z","datePublished":"2011-08-23T01:38:35Z","name":"Graco SnugRide 40","synopsis":"Updated editor's note: Graco discontinued the product in August 2014. Editor's note: Graco in July 2014 announced a recall for the buckle on this baby car se